meta {
  name: Retrieve an identity source user
  type: http
  seq: 20
}

get {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/identity-sources/{{identitySourceId}}/users/{{externalId}}
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Retrieves a user by external ID in an identity source for the given identity source instance

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
